reviewText: Funny stuff and great actors and set design! Definitely keep it up. It's funny like Spliff 16!

Didn't know what to expect from the 'reviews' of this so took a chance. Well, it's Not a kiddie movie at all. Some of the movie has laughs. The so-called 'sci-fi of it isn't worth much, and could have been lots better. Frankly I'd pick something else more interesting.
I saw the screening in NYC and I was hysterical laughing.  Make sure you watch properly prepared!
